intelligentroutingd(8) System Manager's Manual intelligentroutingd(8)

NAME

intelligentroutingd — A daemon that provides recommendations based on history patterns.

DESCRIPTION

intelligentroutingd is a per-user daemon that provides recommendations based on history patterns.

There are no configurations to intelligentroutingd, and users should not run intelligentroutingd manually.
